org.apache.ignite.cache.query

Interface QueryDetailMetrics


  • public interface QueryDetailMetrics
    Query metrics aggregated by query type and its textual representation. Query detail metrics could be enabled via CacheConfiguration.setQueryDetailMetricsSize(int) method.
